yle="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent;border-radius:15px" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/home/product-feature/05 Layanan pelanggan.webp"/></div><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit_text__WnB_8"><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit_title__xandr">Layanan pelanggan</div><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit_description__qZMxX">Customer service kami siap membantumu</div></div></div><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit__zdqGn"><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit_img__large__6Lqtu"><img alt="Bonus Menarik" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent;border-radius:15px" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/home/product-feature/06 Bonus Menarik.webp"/></div><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit_text__WnB_8"><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit_title__xandr">Bonus Menarik</div><div class="ProductBenefits_benefit_description__qZMxX">Tukarkan poinmu dengan beragam bonus menarik.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="UserReviews_user_reviews__sQSE8"><div class="UserReviews_user_reviews_card__VFSzc"><div class="UserReviews_user_reviews_content__uBDc0"><div class="UserReviews_card_title___0B4Q"><div class="UserReviews_quote_img__5k55P"><img alt="quote" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/home/quote.png"/></div><div class="Text_text___N7gX Text_h3__EZtQN UserReviews_text__H9tiI">Apa Kata Pengguna AdaKami ?</div></div><div class="UserReviews_slider_section__N2AdN"><div class="UserReviews_slider_left__F_iQV"><div class="slick-slider UserReviews_user_reviews_slider__HtIEd slick-initialized" dir="ltr"><div class="slick-list"><div class="slick-track" style="width:2100%;left:-100%"><div data-index="0" class="slick-slide slick-active slick-current" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="false" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:0;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Aplikasi AdaKami itu bikin untung banget untuk para penggunanya seperti saya ini karena bisa mendapatkan pinjaman daring secara cepat, dana tunai tanpa ribet dengan berbagai persyaratan yang tetek bengek dan bikin lama prosesnya. Sebab, cairnya gak butuh banyak waktu dan semua data diri saya dijamin aman olehnya karena AdaKami sudah berizin dan diawasi oleh OJK. Jadinya, bikin hati saya menjadi adem ayem untuk bisa fokus pada satu tujuan penggunaan uang pinjaman tersebut. Terima kasih banyak, AdaKami! 💚</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">H</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Heru Dwi S</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="1" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-4px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Desain antarmuka yang ditawarkan oleh aplikasi AdaKami sangat sederhana sehingga mudah dipahami. Sebagai pengguna saya merasa nyaman ketika mengoperasikan aplikasi ini. Proses pendaftaran yang cepat, bisa meminjam dana dengan mudah, dan dijamin anti ribet. Banyak promo untuk mengurangi biaya tagihan, juga tersedia program referral dari AdaKami bagi para debiturnya. Dengan perencanaan yang baik, pinjaman daring dapat menjadi sumber keuangan yang berguna untuk kebutuhan mendesak saya. Terima kasih!</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">N</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Nugraha Ali Sidik</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="2" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-8px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">AdaKami benar-benar solusi saat butuh dana cepat! Proses pengajuannya mudah, pencairannya juga gak ribet. Selama pakai aplikasi ini, semua berjalan lancar tanpa kendala. Bunga dan tenor juga cukup fleksibel, jadi bisa disesuaikan dengan kemampuan bayar. Yang paling penting, #SelaluWaspada terhadap penipuan! Jangan pernah percaya kalau ada yang menawarkan pinjaman lewat WA atau SMS di luar aplikasi resmi. Selalu pakai aplikasi asli biar transaksi aman dan nyaman. Recommended banget! 👍🏼😍</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">A</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Anisa cahya Ramanda</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="3" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-12px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Saya baru banget download AdaKami, pengalamanku setelah menggunakan aplikasi ini aplikasi nya ringan dan gak sampe 50MB. Dan juga aplikasi ini bener-bener memudahkan. Proses pengajuan pinjamannya gampang dan langsung cair tanpa nunggu lama. Tampilan aplikasinya juga simpel dan nggak ribet, jadi gue bisa langsung paham cara gunainnya. 😁</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">V</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Vita Widyastuti</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="4" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-16px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Saya mencoba menggunakan aplikasi AdaKami untuk kebutuhan dana mendesak. Proses pengajuannya tergolong mudah &amp; cepat dengan persyaratan yang cukup jelas. Namun, saya tetap berhati-hati &amp; membaca semua ketentuan dengan saksama sebelum menyetujui pinjaman. Layanan pelanggan juga responsif ketika saya memiliki pertanyaan. Secara keseluruhan, pengalaman saya cukup positif, tetapi saya tetap menyarankan untuk selalu bijak dalam menggunakan layanan pinjaman online &amp; hanya meminjam sesuai kebutuhan.</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">P</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Putri Devina Rosita</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="5" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-20px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Mantap! Sangat rekomen. Proses pengajuan sangat mudah, cukup dengan KTP, satset bisa cair. Bisa pilih tenor sendiri dan bunganya juga rendah. Alhamdulillah, aku sudah cair 2x dan semuanya lancar. Data diri dijamin aman tidak akan dibocorkan kemanapun. Dan pastinya, aman dari tindak penipuan karena CS Resmi AdaKami ada banyak yang bisa dihubungi. Jadi, kalau ada nomor tidak dikenal minta dikirimkan uang, kode OTP, kode PIN lebih baik #SelaluWaspada langsung tanyakan ke CS Resmi AdaKami.</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">D</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">dina kyukyu</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="6" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-24px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">*Pengalaman Menggunakan Aplikasi AdaKami* Sejak pertama kali menggunakan aplikasi AdaKami, hidupku menjadi jauh lebih mudah dan nyaman! Proses pendaftaran yang cepat dan user-friendly membuatku bisa mendapatkan pinjaman dengan mudah saat membutuhkan dana mendesak. Layanan pelanggan yang responsif dan ramah juga sangat membantu dalam menjawab setiap pertanyaanku. Fitur yang disukai: &quot;kemudahan dalam melacak status pinjaman dan proses pembayaran yang simpel</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">D</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Don quisote</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="7" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-28px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Aplikasi AdaKami memudahkan saya saat butuh modal buat berdagang, proses pinjaman cepat, tidak ribet, dan tidak khawatir karena data kita aman, udah dibawah OJK juga. Proses pembayaran juga mudah dengan bunga yang wajar. Jadi, buat yang butuh dana/modal, ga usah ragu lagi buat pakai AdaKami.</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">G</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Gusti Agustini</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="8" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-32px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Saya pernah menerima pesan yang mengaku sebagai Customer Service Adakami yang meminta saya untuk mengirimkan kode verifikasi dan informasi pribadi lainnya. Saya sangat curiga dan tidak mengirimkan informasi apa pun. Setelah itu, saya melaporkan kejadian tersebut kepada pihak Adakami dan mereka sangat cepat merespons dan membantu saya. #SelaluWaspada</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">M</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Male</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_3__n_qJn" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_4__5U62N" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="9" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:4.761904761904762%;position:relative;left:-36px;opacity:0;transition:opacity 500ms ease, visibility 500ms ease"><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card_container__bpSK1"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_review_card__jzsbU"><div class="UserReviewCard_review_content__i5fxj">Download aplikasinya gampang, daftarnya juga gampang. Tinggal ikuti step-stepnya aja 👍 Pencairan dana mudah, CS juga responsif. Limit pinjaman juga sesuai kemampuan. Berdasarkan pengalaman, cukup puas pake Adakami, mudah dan aman 👌</div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile__GpSLJ"><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_image_container__Be5wE"><div class="UserReviewCard_avatar__QZkjC">S</div></div><div><div class="UserReviewCard_user_profile_name__NMKUT">Sundayklwn</div><div class="Rating_rating__pun6d"><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_1__1kfhL" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent" src="https://static.adakami.id/gfe/www/content/images/icons/star.svg"/></div><div class="Rating_star_img__erOrf"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="Rating_star_2__EYQ2v" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;ri